      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "GROUND CONTROL (1) was strongly supported last start when a short priced favourite and duly saluted winning by 2.75 lengths at this track in a handy 18.00. Has the coveted inside box and likes the trip. Solid formlines coming through his last run. Can measure up again. STAN'S DREAM (8) has a strong record this trip with 14 wins and 10 placings from 27 starts. Comes off a (17.86) win last time, scoring by 2.25 lengths in a Grade 1/2 over 312m at this track. Looks one of the chances. DANCE HER HOME (4) led all the way last time out to score by 4 lengths (17.82) at this track in a Grade 3 over 312m. Ran the fastest time on the program in her latest win. Has definite claims. TRUST ME (7) has claims again if he runs up to the latest effort.",
